    "description": "DPLASMA is a highly optimized, accelerator-aware, implementation of a\ndense linear algebra package for distributed heterogeneous systems. It\nis designed to deliver sustained performance for distributed systems\nwhere each node featuring multiple sockets of multicore processors, and\nif available, accelerators, using the PaRSEC runtime as a backend.\n",
